//Tutorial GOT IT Welcome in short tutorial on how to use this app. Click GOT IT! when you ready to see what is next! This is the simplest way to introduce new expression to calculate, deleting a previous content at the same time. But if you want to continue, without deleting… …click CONTINUE button, the previous expressions will be added to what you are going to introduce. In case you are tired with constantly hitting CONTINUE button… …click button LOOP. After each expression you will be given a chance to continue. Until you stop, either with button or by pausing your speech for a long time. Your expressions is shown here while you introducing it, in realtime. You may edit it if you wish to. Your edition is taken on account on next evaluation Here you find the evaluation of above expression Use it to reset the content Use it to stop introducing an expression. Simple, yea? Try it! Replay tutorial
